5 pillars of DevOps
1. Cloud
2. Containers
3. IaaC
4. CI/CD
5. Observability


cloud : AWS
Containers : Docker, K8s
source code : Github
configuration manager : Ansible
CI/CD : Jenkins
IaC : Vagrant, Ansible, Terraform  
Observalibility : prometheus

logs
Elasticsearch - Logstash - Kibana, also called as ELK stack,

metrics
And similarly, for metrics, you have Prometheus and Grafana.


traces
 Jaeger zipkin


Other tools :
Continuse Deployment : Spinnaker (extension for Jenkins for hybrid cloud deployment)
